My new bill, the DC CRIMES Act helps President Trump restore law and order in our nations capital by:

➡️ Making “Youth Offenders” = Under 18 Only
Right now, 18–24 yr olds get lighter “youth” sentences, but this group makes up ¼ of homicides & shooting perpetrators. The bill ends that.

➡️ Ending Loopholes on Sentences
Judges can currently go below mandatory minimums for youth offenders. The bill closes that gap.

➡️ Keeping Sentences Strong
Stops the D.C. Council from rolling back penalties or weakening sentencing guidelines.

➡️ Shining a Light on Juvenile Crime Data
Requires the D.C. Attorney General to post monthly stats: arrests, repeat offenders, sentencing outcomes.

We must act decisively to protect our values and secure a future that honors Indiana’s heartland spirit.
